vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a fire lane easement to Berryset II Uptown BJO, LLC and Berryset II Uptown LTN, LLC, the abutting owners, containing approximately 2,000 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Armstrong and Cole Avenues - Revenue: General Fund $11,150.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
